    <content><![CDATA[<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hSqO8ppMYyc" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
# <center>Trojan+v2ray+SSR单VPS共存</center>
 准备工具：域名1个/VPS一台(CentOS7)
视频教程：[YouTube](https://youtu.be/hSqO8ppMYyc)
1:域名解析到VPS；解析要充分，以便全球生效！

<p>2：安装BBR PLUS加速（可选）</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget <span class="string">"https://github.com/chiakge/Linux-NetSpeed/raw/master/tcp.sh"</span> &amp;&amp; chmod +x tcp.sh &amp;&amp; ./tcp.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>3:大神atrandys一键安装Trojan脚本：<br>若提示无wget,则运行：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum -y install wget</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后再运行下面Docker版Trojan一键安装脚本:</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -O https://raw.githubusercontent.com/atrandys/trojan/master/trojan_install.sh &amp;&amp; chmod +x trojan_install.sh &amp;&amp; ./trojan_install.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>4：运行大神Docker的UI管理Portainer一键脚本：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d -p 9000:9000 -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock \</span><br><span class="line">--name ui --restart=always lihaixin/portainer:me</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>5：浏览器运行<a href="https://VPS_IP:9000;设置密码并创建帐户，然后选择local。">https://VPS_IP:9000;设置密码并创建帐户，然后选择local。</a></p>
<p>6:在容器containers中可以看到安装的Trojan；在App Templates中可以选择V2ray、SSR、Brook等代理程序</p>
<p>8：客户端下载<br><a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=1m9b6n9KnWI40octuo6IWAWqWdWxseLLk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SS客户端</a><br><a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=15sRZ7Sf9CVO0IdELNEvgD7xLxCxMqUVO" target="_blank" rel="noopener">V2ray客户端下载</a></p>
